unittitle_ssm: Archives of Irish America Material Culture and Ephemera Collection
abstract_ssm: The Archives of Irish America (AIA) Material Culture and Ephemera Collection is an artificial collection composed of objects individually donated or found in other AIA collections. The collection consists of various items such as buttons, bumper stickers, hats, tickets, membership cards, pens, pins, musical instruments, and t-shirts -- many of which relate to Irish and Irish American organizations.
